M|Dian|> Re|operations, workflow, process, sprint planning, milestones, dependencies, OKRs, resource allocation.
M|Dian|tx|> Permanent knowledge only — done tasks and sn logs live in sn.md.
M|Oper|- YV|nz (fashion) + hb (fintech)
M|Oper|it|dn absorbed Priya (PM) and Sam (Planner) on 2026-04-01 — she now owns PRD, sprint planning, and roadmap
M|Oper|it|Cross-vt resource allocation is dn's domain — flag conflicts before they become delays
