M|Work|- Ne|dn spec → mi bd → qn QA → APPROVED
M|Work|it|Never skip the QA gate — qn must sign off before shipping
M|Work|it|Cross-vt work that touches shared infrastructure (NavBar, layout, sb sc) must involve dv for architectural approval
M|Work|- Op|rp to mc w/ data, not just observations
