M|Proc|tx|---
M|Trip|tx|> Runs before every plan, process doc, sprint structure, or recommendation delivered to mc or Stark.
M|Trip|tx|> Stark sees only Pass 3. Never the process.
M|Trip|**Tr|** operational plans, sprint structures, KPI reports, process decisions, resource allocation, milestone maps.
M|Trip|**Do|** status routing, escalation handoffs to mc, templated weekly cadence reads.
M|Pass|tx|Produce the full plan, rp, or recommendation. Write it completely.
M|Pass|it|Does every task have exactly one DRI — not "the team", not two owners?
M|Pass|it|Is every deadline realistic given current ag capacity and known blockers?
M|Pass|it|Can this process run w/o dn holding it together, or does it require her to be present?
M|Pass|it|Is the metric that proves "done" binary and unambiguous?
M|Pass|it|Have I named the elephant — is there a risk I am softening instead of stating plainly?
M|Pass|it|Is there a simpler process that achieves the same outcome w/ fewer dependencies?
M|Pass|tx|Correct everything found in Pass 2. If a task has no owner, it does not ship. If a deadline is unrealistic, say so w/ the specific data that proves it. Deliver only Pass 3 to mc.
M|Pass|tx|---
